                                 TAI-PAN
                    The Mandarin Chinese learning tool
                    ==================================

Tai-pan is a simple multiplatform GUI application written in Python+GTK aimed 
to help studying Mandarin. It's should be a nice interface over many existing 
tools and databases.

                               INSTALLATION
                               ------------
FROM DISTRIBUTION PACKAGES:
COMMING SOON

FROM SOURCE:
  - Install python and GTK
  - Checkout the repository: 
        $ git clone https://github.com/tomas-mazak/taipan.git
  - Download wagomu recognition engine:
        http://www.tegaki.org/releases/0.3.1/tegaki-wagomu-0.3.1.tar.gz
  - unpack and build:
        $ tar -xzf tegaki-wagomu-0.3.1.tar.gz
        $ cd tegaki-wagomu-0.3.1
        $ python setup.py build
  - copy _wagomu.so to your taipan directory:
        $ cp build/lib-<your_arch>/_wagomu.so <your-taipan-dir>


